cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DC, cs.DB, cs.CE 

The paper focuses on empirical study of machine learning functionalities provided by major cloud service providers, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The study also involves structured data, which can be related to databases (cs.DB) and distributed computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper presents a novel benchmark, which can be related to computational engineering (cs.CE).
